<body>
  <Navbar />
  <Breadcrumb items={[{text: "Driveway Aprons in North Jersey", href: "/ Services / Concrete / Aprons"}]} />
  <main>
    <Section title="Seamless Transitions That Protect and Enhance Your Driveway">
      <p>Driveway aprons connect your private drive to the public street. At MAC Paving, we install and repair aprons across North Jersey to ensure smooth, strong, and code-compliant transitions.</p>
      <img src="assets/imgs/service/concrete/aprons_1.webp" alt="Driveway Aprons in Northern NJ | Smooth & Durable Transitions - Main Image - MAC Paving and Sealcoating" />
    </Section>
    <Section title="Built for Strength, Slope, and Everyday Use">
      <p>Aprons take heavy wear from vehicles and weather. We use reinforced concrete or asphalt, built for proper slope and resilience. Our aprons align perfectly with street edges and township specs.</p>
      <img src="assets/imgs/service/concrete/aprons_2.webp" alt="Driveway Aprons in Northern NJ | Smooth & Durable Transitions - Side View - MAC Paving and Sealcoating" />
    </Section>
    <Section title="Our Apron Installation Process">
      <p>We remove the old section, prep the base, and pour new asphalt or concrete. Edges are shaped and finished for strength and appearance. Every apron is installed with lasting performance in mind.</p>
      <img src="assets/imgs/service/concrete/aprons_3.webp" alt="Driveway Aprons in Northern NJ | Smooth & Durable Transitions - Close-Up - MAC Paving and Sealcoating" />
    </Section>
    <Section title="Know When It’s Time to Replace or Upgrade">
      <p>If your apron is crumbling or misaligned, it’s time to act. A new apron improves access, drainage, and property value. Contact MAC Paving today for a free evaluation.</p>
      <img src="assets/imgs/service/concrete/aprons_4.webp" alt="Driveway Aprons in Northern NJ | Smooth & Durable Transitions - Work in Progress - MAC Paving and Sealcoating" />
    </Section>
  </main>
